properties.comment: Model parameter definition ========================== Model : Motor Type : Example Parameters ---------- PowerNominal [W] Nominal mechanical power of motor. RotspeedNominal [rpm] Nominal rotational speed of motor. PowerSamples [W] Power samples used for linear interpolation of the efficiency. The PowerSamples must be sorted, smallest value first. RotspeedSamples [rpm] Rotational speed samples used for linear interpolation of the efficiency. The RotspeedSamples must be sorted, smallest value first. EfficiencyMatrix [1] The matrix value at the position p,r (EfficiencyMatrix[p,r]) corresponds to the motor efficiency when the motor is running at power PowerSamples[p] and at rotational speed RotspeedSamples[r].
